    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting. every day is just performing these motions... eating, sleeping, walking around. but there's no spark. no meaning. if the thing that made life worth it is gone, then what's the point of the rest of it? it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own body at this point.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
